quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,Tabahi hai har us shaks ke liye jo (moonh dar moonh) logon par taan aur (peeth peechey) buraiyan karne ka khugar hai
  104,2,Jisne maal jama kiya aur usey gin gin kar rakkha
  104,3,Woh samajhta hai ke us ka maal hamesha uske paas rahega
  104,4,"Hargiz nahin, woh shaks to chakna-chur kar dene wali jagah mein phenk diya jayega"
  104,5,Aur tum kya jano ke kya hai woh chakna-chur kar dene wali jagah
  104,6,Allah ki aag khoob bhadkayi hui
  104,7,Jo dilon tak pahunchey gi
  104,8,Woh un par dhaank kar bandh kar di jayegi
  104,9,(Is halat mei ke woh) unchey unchey sutuno mei (ghirey huey hongey)